FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our purr-fect cat marketplace
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the cat marketplace work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our marketplace connects cat breeders and sellers with potential buyers. Browse listings, contact sellers, and find your ideal feline companion.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Are the cats on your marketplace healthy and vaccinated?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We require all sellers to provide health certificates and vaccination records for their cats. However, we recommend buyers to verify this information independently.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I return a cat if it's not a good fit?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Each seller has their own return policy. We encourage you to discuss this with the seller before making a purchase. Our platform prioritizes the well-being of all cats.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How do I list my cat for sale on your marketplace?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Create an account, verify your identity, and follow our listing guidelines. Make sure to include clear photos, detailed descriptions, and health information about your cat.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Is there a fee for using the marketplace?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Browsing is free for buyers. Sellers pay a small listing fee and a commission on successful sales. Check our pricing page for current rates.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Cat Marketplace
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the cat marketplace work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our cat marketplace connects cat breeders and sellers with potential buyers. Users can browse listings, view cat profiles, and contact sellers directly through our platform to arrange purchases or adoptions.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What types of cats are available on your marketplace?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We offer a wide variety of cats, including purebred, mixed breed, and rescue cats. You can find kittens, adult cats, and senior cats of various breeds, colors, and personalities to suit your preferences.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How do I ensure the cat I'm interested in is healthy?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: All sellers on our platform are required to provide up-to-date health certificates and vaccination records for their cats. We also encourage buyers to schedule vet check-ups before finalizing any purchase or adoption.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if I have issues with my cat purchase?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We have a customer support team dedicated to resolving any issues that may arise during or after your cat purchase. We also offer a satisfaction guarantee and can assist with returns or exchanges in certain situations.
